Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw arrived at Predacon cave. She flew from a distance, 
stopping to look at it. She was here before. She was here when the 
large bot at the same Predacon ship gave here the cooridinates where 
Megatron was. 

She shrugged it off and flew down to the front of it. 

She called, "Who here is KitKat? I was sent by Black Arachnia fron 
the Predacon base."
